â€œHello adventurers, would you like to take a look at my products? I also have two specials for today.

The first is a set of four exquisite magic rings that I made recently, they are yours for 600g, only if you buy all four.

The second is this unidentified magic ring, it is yours for 250g, to know what it does you will have to equip it when you buy it."
